# Frontend React

- Build UI with typed functional components and keep logic inside feature folders (e.g., `frontend/src/features/...`).
- Derive state via hooks, lift only when necessary, and use React Query for server data.
- Validate form inputs with shared schema definitions when available and keep validation close to the form.
- Prefer design-system primitives and consistent Tailwind utility ordering.
- Keep styling/configuration (Tailwind, Vite) centralized and documented; avoid inline `style` overrides.
